        </noscript>
        </a>
        <figcaption style="height:0;opacity:0;">Workers disembark a research vessel docked in San Diego in June 2021.</figcaption>
    </figure>
    <div class="list-text">
        <a
    class="hed-heading -excerpt"
    href="https://foreignpolicy.com/2023/11/20/china-deep-sea-mining-critical-mineral-energy-transition-isa/">
    <h3 class="hed">China Aims to Corner the Undersea Mineral Market, Too</h3>
</a>
<div class="dek-heading -excerpt">
    <p class="dek">The race is on to tap the riches of minerals in the high seas.</p>
</div>
