        <a
    class="hed-heading -excerpt"
    href="https://foreignpolicy.com/2023/11/04/elon-musk-is-the-messy-hero-of-our-messy-age/">
    <h3 class="hed">Elon Musk Is the Messy Hero of Our Messy Age</h3>
</a>
<div class="dek-heading -excerpt">
    <p class="dek">For better and worse, he represents how change happens in our current society.</p>
</div>
<div class="meta-data -excerpt">
        <a
        href="https://foreignpolicy.com/category/review/"
        class="department-name -excerpt ">
        Review    </a>
        <p class="separator" aria-hidden="true">|</p>
        <address class="author-list -excerpt">
    <a
        href="https://foreignpolicy.com/author/zachary-karabell/"
        data-author-id="398357"        class="author">
    Zachary Karabell</a></address>

</div>
    </div>
</div>
        </div>

