<a
    class="hed-heading -excerpt"
    href="https://foreignpolicy.com/2023/10/23/turkey-erdogan-dams-water-construction-corruption-environment-economy/">
    <h3 class="hed">King of the Dammed</h3>
</a>
<div class="dek-heading -excerpt">
    <p class="dek">Turkish President Erdogan’s mega-infrastructure projects are enriching construction companies while reshaping his country’s waterscape for the worse.</p>
</div>
<div class="meta-data -excerpt">
    <address class="author-list -excerpt">
    <a
        href="https://foreignpolicy.com/author/hannah-lucinda-smith/"
        data-author-id="1127687"        class="author">
    Hannah Lucinda Smith</a></address>

